SHE may have attracted her fair share of criticism for her extravagant lifestyle but that hasn t stopped socialite and businesswoman Uyanda Mbuli from making career strides outside the borders of South Africa.The Mpumalanga-born media personality s determination has scored her an exclusive invite to the University of Buckingham in England.Mbuli is set to speak at International Talks, an event organised by the university s social and academics club, on June 16.This is not just any event but one that invites influencers from around the globe. The entertainer and businesswoman is set to be welcomed by Buckingham mayor Jon Harvey.NONTOKOZO GXUMISA